data.description: Welcome to 301 W Gov Miro! FLOOD ZONE X, 2-year-old roof and AC!! $6,000 credit to be used toward flooring or rate buy-down, whatever you'd like!! This 4-bedroom 2-bathroom home provides more space than imaginable. With 2 bedrooms downstairs and 2 bedrooms upstairs, this split floorplan is sure to wow! Did we mention the formal dining, formal living, and den addition? There is enough space for everyone when entertaining in the heart of Lafayette. Hardwood floors downstairs, a fireplace, and a massive drop zone in the laundry are just a few of the bells and whistles this updated home has to offer. Be sure to schedule a showing while it's fresh on the market!
